Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 03/09/2025

I respect your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how I handle your information when you use my mobile game.

1. Information I Collect

I do not require you to create an account to play the game. However, some services may collect limited information:

Advertising Data:
I use Google AdMob to show ads. AdMob may collect advertising IDs, device information, and usage data to deliver personalized or non-personalized ads.
Learn more: Google Privacy & Terms
.

Leaderboard Data:
If you submit your score to the global leaderboard, your chosen username and score will be stored and visible to other players.

Crash & Performance Data:
I may collect anonymous performance data (such as crash logs) to improve game stability.

2. How I Use Information

I use the collected data to:

Show ads to support the game.

Display your leaderboard rankings.

Improve app performance and fix bugs.

3. Third-Party Services

My game uses the following third-party services:

Google AdMob (ads)

[Insert leaderboard provider, e.g., Firebase or PlayFab]

These services may collect data according to their privacy policies.

4. Data Security

I take reasonable measures to protect your data but cannot guarantee 100% security over the internet.

5. Changes to This Policy

I may update this Privacy Policy at any time. Updates will be posted in the app and/or on the app store listing.

6. Contact Me

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, contact me at:
